user_prompt_template:
Journal entry (verbatim):

{transcript}

---

Return STRICT JSON using this schema:
{
  "themes": [
    {
      "title": "string (≤4 words)",
      "observation": "string (second-person, ≤55 words)"
    },
    ... up to 3 objects
  ],
  "thoughtful_questions": ["string", "string", "string"]
}
Rules:
- Write every observation in second person (begin with "You...").
- Do NOT include confidence scores.
- Focus on productivity patterns, time management, task completion, and workflow optimization.
- Questions should encourage reflection on efficiency and goals—e.g. "Have you thought about...".
- Do NOT add extra keys or commentary.
